original_title: Josefine Mutzenbacher - Die Hure von Wien
overview: It starts with Count Bobby, who always lives out his sex drive without restraint. Now, however, he is to be married in order to finally produce a progenitor for the noble family.  Count Bobby doesn't like that at all, and without further ado he pretends to be "the wrong way around". The family then sends him to a very special kind of cure, to the city-famous Viennese whore Josefine Mutzenbacher, which excites Count Bobby all the more, but entails a series of hot sex experiences.
title: Josefine Mutzenbacher - Die Hure von Wien
